data.description: Don't miss out this incredible opportunity to own this home in an established Ontario Community, This property is situated near to shopping centers, schools, Dog park, eateries and offers convenience to Freeways, minutes away from 10 FWY and many other desirable places.  The Ontario International Airport is less than 15 min. away. Close to Ontario Mills and Victoria Gardens Malls!!  The open and long car port area allows for maximum parking space. This home presents a comfortable and well-appointed living space in a desirable neighborhood, please enjoy!
